title: The Eagles - Inglewood (Deluxe 2-CD) 1980 ak
description:
The Eagles - Inglewood (Deluxe 2-CD) 1980 ak
Just Before and during and some even after this was the Last tour until Hell freezes over. 1994 So its too bad some real good stuff came from almost all of them during the long hiatus. Anyway I have been busy collecting all kinds of material and will kick it down when its time.
Speaking of time its the beginning of my 5th year uploading. Jan 1 2014.

The rest of the band also has set the dates for the 2018 tour
so go see em before they disappear. No one is getting any younger
